description_for_model:
Plugin to run Replicate models
Popular models are:
replicate/llama-7b, ai-forever/kandinsky-2, cjwbw/stable-diffusion-v2.1 (Stable diffusion 2), stability-ai/stable-diffusion (or 'SD', for stable diffusion 1.5), cjwbw/damo-text-to-video, rossjillian/controlnet (For stable diffusion 1.5), rossjillian/controlnet_2-1 (For stable diffusion 2.1), cjwbw/semantic-segment-anything, salesforce/blip, 
Other popular diffusion models include: cjwbw/anything-v4.0 (anime images), prompthero/openjourney, deforum/deforum_stable_diffusion for making animations from prompts
